race.description: Greyhounds As Pets Mixed Stake Cta Division1
race.comment: WOODSIDE JOHNNY (7) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 530m behind Bourne Model (31.21) in a OPEN. Placed at his previous run. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Should bounce back. MUNDULLA (1) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 530m behind Galactic Nemesis (31.33) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. Worth another chance. BUSTER BRADY (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (31.01) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. The form from his last run stacks up well. One of the better chances. FANTASTIC SPIKE (8) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.
